> where can i get more scenarios

Two responses:

1)check the files section of this Yahoo Group for scenarios.

2)Look in the mirror if you want someone to create more scenarios if 
you are unwilling to give feedback.

Beyond that, the 50 Project (creating 50 brand-new scenarios from 
stratch) will come up sooner or later again.  Frankly, I don't have 
the time to work out more details with the plot, but if someone does 
want to expand the plot enough where we can start creating the 
scenarios, let me know.
